graph.original_query: ### Generate a Beautiful Multi-Page Landing Website using Flowbite (Dark Mode)Create a **dark-themed, modern landing website** using **Flowbite + Tailwind CSS**.The site should have 4 pages:* `index.html` (Home)* `about.html`* `products.html`* `contact.html`‚úÖ **Site Requirements**#### üåå Theme* Use **Flowbite** with **Tailwind CSS** in **dark mode*** Ensure consistency in fonts, spacing, and responsiveness* Include dark background and high-contrast elements#### üìÑ Pages and Structure1. **index.html (Home)** * Full-screen hero section with background image (from Unsplash or other safe public image sources) * Features section (3‚Äì4 highlights) * Testimonials section (dark cards) * CTA section (‚ÄúStart Free Trial‚Äù or similar) * Footer with social icons + links2. **about.html** * Mission statement * Timeline or values section * Team member cards3. **products.html** * Grid layout with 6‚Äì8 product/service cards * Each card has title, short description, image, price (if relevant) * Filter or category tags optional4. **contact.html** * Contact form with name/email/message * Map placeholder or location card * Email and support links#### üñºÔ∏è Image Guidance* Use image URLs from: * [Unsplash](https://source.unsplash.com) * [Pexels](https://www.pexels.com/) * [Picsum](https://picsum.photos)Example:```html```#### üß© Tech Notes* Use Tailwind + Flowbite CDN setup (no build tools required)* Keep layout modular: shared header/footer across pages* Add `` tags and page titles properly* Ensure mobile responsiveness---### üì¶ Output FormatPlease generate 4 code blocks, one per file:```html...``````html...```...Use real, readable English content ‚Äì not placeholders.The goal is to make the site **look and feel like a real premium product launch site**. Call CoderAgent atleast 10 times for different exhaustive tasks as this is a detailed project.---
